            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Toi qui, sur le frêle navire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Où nous voguons, as mis du lest",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Dans la crainte qu'il ne chavire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Inspire-moi, sublime Ernest !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Toi qui, sur le frêle navire\nOù nous voguons, as mis du lest\nDans la crainte qu'il ne chavire,\nInspire-moi, sublime Ernest !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Tu communiques ! Communique-",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Moi tes sentiments fanfarons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Un vocable te semble inique ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Il suffit. Avec lui je romps !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tu communiques ! Communique-\nMoi tes sentiments fanfarons.\nUn vocable te semble inique ?\nIl suffit. Avec lui je romps !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Dût le style en devenir terne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "J'écrirai sur un ton gaillard,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Au lieu du mot qui rime en terne :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Interrompu par le brouillard,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dût le style en devenir terne,\nJ'écrirai sur un ton gaillard,\nAu lieu du mot qui rime en terne :\nInterrompu par le brouillard,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Ou bien quelque autre synonyme.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Je commence, dût à mes yeux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Expirer de chagrin la Rime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Car le plus tôt sera le mieux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ou bien quelque autre synonyme.\nJe commence, dût à mes yeux\nExpirer de chagrin la Rime,\nCar le plus tôt sera le mieux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Au boulevard, les candélabres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "J'en saute, comme Eugène Paz !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Portent au haut de leurs fûts glabres",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Des Inexpressibles — à gaz.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au boulevard, les candélabres,\nJ'en saute, comme Eugène Paz !\nPortent au haut de leurs fûts glabres\nDes Inexpressibles — à gaz."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Diogène, âme peu commune,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "S'il vient chercher son homme ici,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "A sa main ne tiendra plus qu'une",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Si j'ose m'exprimer ainsi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Diogène, âme peu commune,\nS'il vient chercher son homme ici,\nA sa main ne tiendra plus qu'une\nSi j'ose m'exprimer ainsi."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Par cette chaleur accablante,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Si Thérèse, dans son château,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Nous offre une fête galante",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Empruntée au charmant Wateau,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Par cette chaleur accablante,\nSi Thérèse, dans son château,\nNous offre une fête galante\nEmpruntée au charmant Wateau,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Les charmilles patriciennes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Empliront de flamme avec des",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Je ne sais quoi — vénitiennes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Leurs feuillages qui font un dais !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les charmilles patriciennes\nEmpliront de flamme avec des\nJe ne sais quoi — vénitiennes\nLeurs feuillages qui font un dais !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Si quelqu'un, se mettant à l'aise,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Veut conter, — on prend ce qu'on a,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "L'histoire du gars de Falaise",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Qu'on trouve dans tous les ana :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si quelqu'un, se mettant à l'aise,\nVeut conter, — on prend ce qu'on a,\nL'histoire du gars de Falaise\nQu'on trouve dans tous les ana :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Pour terminer, s'il veut qu'en somme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Ernest ne le tourmente point,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Il devra dire : Le pauvre homme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "N'avait donc omis qu'un seul point,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour terminer, s'il veut qu'en somme\nErnest ne le tourmente point,\nIl devra dire : Le pauvre homme\nN'avait donc omis qu'un seul point,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "C'est d'allumer sa — Trois-Étoiles.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi, comme la mer à Brest,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Gonflez-vous, doux et légers voiles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Pour plaire à la pudeur d'Ernest !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est d'allumer sa — Trois-Étoiles.\nAinsi, comme la mer à Brest,\nGonflez-vous, doux et légers voiles,\nPour plaire à la pudeur d'Ernest !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Oui, désormais, l'amant qui raille",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Dans le drame de Bouchardy,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "L'homme au manteau couleur muraille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Le Mélingue fier et hardi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oui, désormais, l'amant qui raille\nDans le drame de Bouchardy,\nL'homme au manteau couleur muraille,\nLe Mélingue fier et hardi"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Aura (ce n'est point une bourde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Émise par quelque Gascon)",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Une Passez-moi le mot — sourde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Pour escalader le balcon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Aura (ce n'est point une bourde\nÉmise par quelque Gascon)\nUne Passez-moi le mot — sourde,\nPour escalader le balcon."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Nous dirons, exempts d'arguties,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Ou chacun s'en repentirait,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "N'allez pas prendre les vessies",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Pour des… — Points suspensifs, tiret !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous dirons, exempts d'arguties,\nOu chacun s'en repentirait,\nN'allez pas prendre les vessies\nPour des… — Points suspensifs, tiret !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Et l'on va sous une funèbre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Feuille de vigne, — du moins tout",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Me le dit, — cacher la célèbre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Comment dirai-je ? — de Saint-Cloud.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et l'on va sous une funèbre\nFeuille de vigne, — du moins tout\nMe le dit, — cacher la célèbre\nComment dirai-je ? — de Saint-Cloud."
